---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="For Suppliers — Ayris Global"
  description="Ayris Global partners with certified Indian botanical producers to connect their ingredients with global wellness buyers. If you produce GMP-certified herbs, extracts, powders, or essential oils, we'd like to hear from you."
>

  <!-- HowTo JSON-LD Schema (Session 28) -->
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={`{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"HowTo","name":"How to Become an Ayris Global Supplier Partner","description":"How certified Indian botanical producers can apply to become a supplier partner with Ayris Global and reach global wellness ingredient buyers.","step":[{"@type":"HowToStep","position":1,"name":"Send Your Product Overview","text":"Email partnerships@ayrisglobal.in with the supplier's product range, certifications held, and production capacity. A brief company profile and product list is enough to start."},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":2,"name":"We Review and Respond","text":"Ayris Global reviews every enquiry within 5 working days and responds with an honest assessment of fit. If there is potential, a call is scheduled to understand the supplier's products and capabilities in more detail."},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":3,"name":"Product Review and Documentation Check","text":"Ayris Global requests samples and a full documentation package, including Certificate of Analysis, certifications, and specification sheets, and evaluates these against current buyer requirements."},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":4,"name":"Partnership Agreement and Market Activation","text":"If the fit is right, Ayris Global formalises the partnership with a simple agreement covering exclusivity scope, commission structure, and working protocols, then begins introducing the supplier's products to relevant buyers."}]}`} slot="head" />

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero__inner">
      <span class="eyebrow">For Indian Producers</span>
      <h1 class="page-hero__title">Your ingredients. Global markets.</h1>
      <p class="page-hero__sub">India produces some of the finest certified botanical ingredients in the world. The challenge is reaching the right buyers — in the right markets — with the right documentation and positioning. That's what Ayris Global does for its supplier partners.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE PROBLEM WE SOLVE -->
  <section class="problem">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="problem__inner">
        <div class="problem__text">
          <span class="section-eyebrow">The Challenge</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">Good producers deserve global reach</h2>
          <p>India has exceptional botanical producers. GMP-certified facilities. Organic-certified farms. Producers who have invested years in building quality systems, getting the right certifications, and perfecting their products. But too many of them remain invisible to the global buyers who would gladly source from them.</p>
          <p>International buyers struggle to find reliable Indian suppliers. They don't know which certifications to trust. They can't evaluate producers remotely. They lack the on-ground knowledge to distinguish an exceptional facility from a mediocre one.</p>
          <p>Ayris Global bridges that gap. We know the Indian botanical supply chain. We know which producers are worth representing. And we have the buyer relationships — across the EU, UK, USA, UAE/GCC, Japan, Korea, ANZ, Southeast Asia, and Latin America — to put your ingredients in front of the right people.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="problem__stats">
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat__num">9</span>
            <span class="stat__label">Global markets we actively supply</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat__num">6</span>
            <span class="stat__label">Ingredient categories we represent</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat__num">0</span>
            <span class="stat__label">Upfront cost to supplier partners</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat__num">100%</span>
            <span class="stat__label">Commission-based — we earn when you earn</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT WE LOOK FOR -->
  <section class="criteria">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header section-header--light">
        <span class="section-eyebrow section-eyebrow--gold">Who We Partner With</span>
        <h2 class="section-title section-title--white">What we look for in a supplier partner</h2>
        <p class="section-sub section-sub--light">We are selective. We represent producers whose quality and certification standards genuinely match what global buyers require. Here's what that looks like.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="criteria-grid">
        <div class="criterion">
          <span class="criterion__num">01</span>
          <h3>Verifiable certifications</h3>
          <p>GMP, ISO 22000, FSSAI as a minimum. Organic (NPOP/NOP), Halal, and Kosher are significant advantages. All certifications must be current, from recognised certifying bodies, and available for buyer review.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="criterion">
          <span class="criterion__num">02</span>
          <h3>Third-party tested product</h3>
          <p>CoA from an accredited independent laboratory — covering active content, microbiological limits, heavy metals, and pesticide residues. Buyers in regulated markets will require this before any purchase decision.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="criterion">
          <span class="criterion__num">03</span>
          <h3>Sample capability</h3>
          <p>Ability to dispatch samples promptly — within 5–7 working days of request. Samples should be accompanied by a full technical data sheet. Buyers make purchasing decisions based on sample evaluation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="criterion">
          <span class="criterion__num">04</span>
          <h3>Consistent supply</h3>
          <p>Ability to fulfil repeat orders at consistent quality across batches. International buyers build formulation programmes around their ingredient supply — supply chain reliability is non-negotiable for long-term partnerships.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="criterion">
          <span class="criterion__num">05</span>
          <h3>Export experience or readiness</h3>
          <p>Experience with export documentation — or willingness to work with a clearing and forwarding agent. Phytosanitary certificates, certificates of origin, and export compliance are prerequisites for international shipments.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="criterion">
          <span class="criterion__num">06</span>
          <h3>Responsive communication</h3>
          <p>The ability to respond promptly to buyer queries — specifications, pricing, lead times, custom requirements. International buyers operate across time zones and expect timely, professional communication.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT WE OFFER SUPPLIERS -->
  <section class="offer">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-eyebrow">What You Get</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">What Ayris Global brings to the partnership</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="offer-grid">
        <div class="offer-item">
          <h3>Global buyer access</h3>
          <p>Direct access to qualified buyers across the EU, UK, USA, UAE/GCC, Japan, Korea, ANZ, Southeast Asia, and Latin America — buyers who are actively looking for Indian botanical ingredients and have the procurement budget to act.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="offer-item">
          <h3>Market-matched positioning</h3>
          <p>We understand what each market needs — which certifications matter, which specifications are standard, how to frame Indian-origin ingredients for different buyer cultures. We position your products correctly for each market.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="offer-item">
          <h3>Documentation support</h3>
          <p>We help you ensure your documentation package meets the requirements of your target markets — and we communicate clearly with buyers about what is available and what can be obtained.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="offer-item">
          <h3>No upfront cost</h3>
          <p>We operate on a commission basis. We earn when you earn. There are no listing fees, no marketing charges, no upfront payments. Our incentive is entirely aligned with generating real commercial outcomes for you.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="offer-item">
          <h3>Serious buyer qualification</h3>
          <p>We don't send you tyre-kickers. Before we connect a buyer with a supplier, we qualify the enquiry — market, volume, specification, timeline, budget. The introductions we make are commercially meaningful.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="offer-item">
          <h3>Long-term relationship</h3>
          <p>We are building a portfolio of suppliers we can represent with confidence over years. We invest in understanding your product range, your capabilities, and your ambitions — and we grow with you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CATEGORIES WE REPRESENT -->
  <section class="categories">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header section-header--light">
        <span class="section-eyebrow section-eyebrow--gold">Product Categories</span>
        <h2 class="section-title section-title--white">What we represent</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="categories-grid">
        <div class="category-item">
          <span class="category-item__num">01</span>
          <h3>Ayurvedic Ingredients</h3>
          <p>Ashwagandha, Shatavari, Brahmi, Triphala, Guduchi, and the full range of classical Ayurvedic botanicals — in extract, powder, and standardised forms.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="category-item">
          <span class="category-item__num">02</span>
          <h3>Herbal Extracts</h3>
          <p>HPLC-standardised botanical extracts with defined active content — supplied as dry powders or liquid extracts with full analytical documentation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="category-item">
          <span class="category-item__num">03</span>
          <h3>Botanical Powders</h3>
          <p>Whole-plant and single-part botanical powders — dried, milled, and sieved to specification. Conventional, organic, and spray-dried formats.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="category-item">
          <span class="category-item__num">04</span>
          <h3>Nutraceutical Ingredients</h3>
          <p>Active botanical ingredients for supplement and functional food applications — curcumin, piperine, and plant-derived actives with clinical validation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="category-item">
          <span class="category-item__num">05</span>
          <h3>Essential Oils</h3>
          <p>Steam-distilled, cold-pressed, and CO₂-extracted botanical oils — GC/MS tested, batch certified. Spice oils, floral absolutes, and medicinal plant oils.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="category-item">
          <span class="category-item__num">06</span>
          <h3>Natural Wellness Ingredients</h3>
          <p>Edible botanicals, functional flowers, and wellness-grade plant ingredients — rose petals, hibiscus, chamomile, tulsi, and dried botanical blends.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW TO APPLY -->
  <section class="apply">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="apply__inner">
        <div class="apply__text">
          <span class="section-eyebrow">Get Started</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">How to become an Ayris Global supplier partner</h2>
          <p>We review every supplier enquiry personally. The process is straightforward — no lengthy forms, no upfront commitments. We start with a conversation, then move to product review if there's a fit.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="apply__steps">
          <div class="apply-step">
            <span class="apply-step__num">1</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Send us your product overview</h4>
              <p>Email us at <a href="mailto:partnerships@ayrisglobal.in">partnerships@ayrisglobal.in</a> with your product range, certifications held, and production capacity. A brief company profile and product list is enough to start.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="apply-step">
            <span class="apply-step__num">2</span>
            <div>
              <h4>We review and respond</h4>
              <p>We review every enquiry within 5 working days and respond with our honest assessment of fit. If we see potential, we'll schedule a call to understand your products and capabilities in more detail.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="apply-step">
            <span class="apply-step__num">3</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Product review and documentation check</h4>
              <p>We'll request samples and a full documentation package — CoA, certifications, specification sheets. We evaluate these against what our current buyers are looking for.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="apply-step">
            <span class="apply-step__num">4</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Partnership agreement and market activation</h4>
              <p>If the fit is right, we formalise the partnership with a simple agreement covering exclusivity scope, commission structure, and working protocols. Then we start introducing your products to relevant buyers.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-band">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-band__inner">
        <h2 class="cta-band__title">Ready to reach global buyers?</h2>
        <p class="cta-band__sub">Send us your product range and certifications. We'll tell you within 5 working days whether there's a fit — and what we can do for you.</p>
        <a href="mailto:partnerships@ayrisglobal.in" class="btn btn--primary btn--lg">Email partnerships@ayrisglobal.in</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    background: #1B2B4B;
    padding: 7rem 1.5rem 5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .page-hero__inner { max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .eyebrow {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.28em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(201,168,76,0.75);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .page-hero__title {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 3.4rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #FAFAF8;
    margin: 0 0 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }
  .page-hero__sub {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: rgba(250,250,248,0.75);
    line-height: 1.82;
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .container { max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; }

  .section-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3.5rem; }
  .section-header--light { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3.5rem; }
  .section-eyebrow {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #C9A84C;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .section-eyebrow--gold { color: #C9A84C; }
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #1B2B4B;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .section-title--white { color: #FAFAF8; }
  .section-sub {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #555;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }
  .section-sub--light { color: rgba(250,250,248,0.65); }

  /* PROBLEM */
  .problem { background: #FAFAF8; padding: 6rem 0; }
  .problem__inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .problem__text .section-eyebrow { margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .problem__text .section-title { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .problem__text p {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #444;
    line-height: 1.82;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }
  .problem__stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    padding-top: 4.8rem;
  }
  .stat {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid rgba(27,43,75,0.09);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 1.5rem 1.1rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .stat__num {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: #C9A84C;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .stat__label {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  /* CRITERIA */
  .criteria { background: #1B2B4B; padding: 6rem 0; }
  .criteria-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .criterion {
    background: rgba(250,250,248,0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.14);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 1.75rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .criterion__num {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: rgba(201,168,76,0.3);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .criterion h3 {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #FAFAF8;
    margin: 0 0 0.7rem;
  }
  .criterion p {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.855rem;
    color: rgba(250,250,248,0.62);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* OFFER */
  .offer { background: #fff; padding: 6rem 0; }
  .offer-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  .offer-item {
    background: #FAFAF8;
    border: 1px solid rgba(27,43,75,0.08);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 1.75rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .offer-item h3 {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #1B2B4B;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
  }
  .offer-item p {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.78;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* CATEGORIES */
  .categories { background: #1B2B4B; padding: 6rem 0; }
  .categories-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .category-item {
    border-top: 2px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.3);
    padding-top: 1.25rem;
  }
  .category-item__num {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: rgba(201,168,76,0.6);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .category-item h3 {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #FAFAF8;
    margin: 0 0 0.6rem;
  }
  .category-item p {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: rgba(250,250,248,0.58);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* APPLY */
  .apply { background: #FAFAF8; padding: 6rem 0; }
  .apply__inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.4fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .apply__text .section-eyebrow { margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .apply__text .section-title { margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .apply__text p {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .apply__steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.75rem; }
  .apply-step {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 44px 1fr;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .apply-step__num {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #1B2B4B;
    color: #C9A84C;
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .apply-step h4 {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #1B2B4B;
    margin: 0 0 0.4rem;
  }
  .apply-step p {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.855rem;
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.72;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .apply-step a {
    color: #C9A84C;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .apply-step a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  /* CTA */
  .cta-band {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1B2B4B 0%, #243655 100%);
    padding: 6rem 0;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .cta-band__inner { max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .cta-band__title {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #FAFAF8;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }
  .cta-band__sub {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: rgba(250,250,248,0.7);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin: 0 0 2.2rem;
  }
  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 0.85rem 1.8rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }
  .btn--primary { background: #C9A84C; color: #1B2B4B; border: 2px solid #C9A84C; }
  .btn--primary:hover { background: #b8922a; border-color: #b8922a; }
  .btn--lg { padding: 1rem 2.2rem; font-size: 0.9rem; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .problem__inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
    .problem__stats { padding-top: 0; }
    .criteria-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .offer-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .categories-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .apply__inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .criteria-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .offer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .categories-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .problem__stats { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }
</style>
